00:18:27,620 --> 00:18:31,440
Okay,yes,I took her clothes,
but she started it...
好吧 是的 我拿了她的衣服
但是她先开火的...

304
00:18:31,470 --> 00:18:35,550
No,that's not fair.
不 这不公平

305
00:18:35,600 --> 00:18:38,190
Why should I have to apologize?
为什么要我去道歉?

306
00:18:38,200 --> 00:18:43,220
Yeah,I really don't think this is the
kind of thing Jesus concerns himself with.
我不认为耶稣会管这等闲事

307
00:18:43,230 --> 00:18:47,000
No,you're right. I don't really
know what Jesus thinks about.
不 你说的对 我真的不知道耶稣在想什么

308
00:18:47,010 --> 00:18:52,340
All right,good-bye.
好吧 再见

309
00:18:53,000 --> 00:18:54,510
Did you tell on me?
是你告的密?

310
00:18:54,520 --> 00:19:00,000
Are you kidding me? I
already have two strikes.
开什么玩笑? 我都已经二振了

311
00:19:03,990 --> 00:19:09,700
Penny. Penny. Penny.
Penny Penny Penny

312
00:19:10,700 --> 00:19:13,990
I am very,very sorry
for what I have done.
非常非常抱歉 为我的行为道歉

313
00:19:14,020 --> 00:19:15,330
Here's your laundry.
这是你的衣服

314
00:19:15,360 --> 00:19:20,390
I rescind your strikes and
you are no longer banished.
我废除了你的记录 你不再被驱逐了

315
00:19:20,400 --> 00:19:23,590
Can I sit wherever I want?
我想坐哪就坐哪了不?

316
00:19:24,880 --> 00:19:28,460
Never mind,never mind.
That's,that's not important.
没事 没事 这个--这个不重要

317
00:19:28,470 --> 00:19:31,330
Sheldon,this was big of you.
Thank you. I really appreciate it.
Sheldon 你真的很宽宏大量
谢谢你 我很感激

318
00:19:31,340 --> 00:19:33,120
Thank you.
谢谢

319
00:19:33,140 --> 00:19:35,880
- Good night,Sheldon.
- Penny...
- 晚安 Sheldon
- Penny...

320
00:19:35,890 --> 00:19:40,300
- Yes?
- Well played.
- 啥?
- 你有一手

321
00:19:42,190 --> 00:19:43,130
Thank you.
谢谢

322
00:19:43,160 --> 00:19:48,950
Just rember: with great power
comes great responsibility.
但请记住 能力越大 责任越大
(出自<蜘蛛侠>)

323
00:19:50,390 --> 00:19:54,600
Understood.
明白

324
00:20:06,640 --> 00:20:07,980
Can I help you?
有什么事吗?

325
00:20:08,010 --> 00:20:11,570
Yes,we're here to fix the cable.
我们是来修有线电视的

326
00:20:11,580 --> 00:20:15,130
I think we have satellite.
我想我们装的是卫星的

327
00:20:15,140 --> 00:20:18,120
That's what I meant.
我说的就是卫星

328
00:20:18,470 --> 00:20:22,060
Okay,come on in.
好吧 请进

329
00:20:25,680 --> 00:20:30,960
She's taller than all the
women in my family combined.
她比我家里女人摞一起都高

330
00:20:31,540 --> 00:20:35,560
What do we do now?
我们接下来干什么?

331
00:20:35,570 --> 00:20:38,750
Follow Mrs. Wolowitz.
跟着Wolowitz太太走呗

